From Tokyo, Japan to the bright lights of Las Vegas, no fighter has captured the intensity and pure power of mixed martial arts like Quinton 'Rampage' Jackson. Now, for the first time ever, the pivotal fights of the UFC superstar's amazing career are collected in Rampage Greatest Hits. Featuring his trademark slams and devastating knockouts, this Blu-ray collects the best of Rampage from PRIDE and the UFC. Watch as he battles the best fighters ever to compete in MMA, such as Chuck 'The Iceman' Liddell, Wanderlei 'The Axe Murderer' Silva, and Kevin 'The Monster' Randleman. This is one collection no fight fan can miss.
